🎮 Pinball Game

A simple and exciting Pinball Game built using Python and Pygame. Bounce the ball, hit bumpers, and rack up points! This project demonstrates basic game physics, collision detection, and interactive graphics

🧩 Features

Classic pinball mechanics

Ball physics and collisions

Score tracking

Sound effects

Game over and restart functionality



---

🚀 Getting Started

Prerequisites

Python 3.x

Pygame library


Install Pygame using pip:

pip install pygame


---

🛠️ How to Run

1. Clone this repository or download the source code.


2. Navigate to the project folder.


3. Run the Python file:



python pinball.py


---

🎮 Controls

Left Arrow / A – Left flipper

Right Arrow / D – Right flipper

Spacebar – Launch ball

R – Restart game



